{"word":"ὄσσομαι","slug":"ὄσσομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n75576\" key=\"o)/ssomai\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὄσσομαι</orth>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ὄσσε</etym>) <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> Verb, used only in <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ pres.\">pres.</a></tns> and <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ impf.\">impf.</a></tns> without augm., <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ pres.\">pres.</a></tns> (I.-<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> </bibl> <sense id=\"n75576.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">oq[uglide]-yo-</tr_>) corresponding to <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ fut.\">fut.</a></tns> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὄψομαι</foreign> (v. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὄψ</foreign>) : <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Act.\">Act.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὄσσω</foreign> only <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4099.tlg001:562:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ EM\">EM</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">562.6</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4099.tlg001:673:11\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">673.11</biblScope> </bibl> : prop. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">see, look,</tr_> as in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:318\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.318</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὄμμασι λοξὸν ὑποδρὰξ ὀσσομένη</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Call.\">Call.</a></author> </bibl> </cit> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.anon.\">Fr.anon.</a></tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0147.tlg001:63\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">63</biblScope></bibl>, and in the compd. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">προτιόσσομαι</foreign> (q.v.) : but mostly, </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n75576.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">see in spirit</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">with the mind's eye,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὀσσόμενος πατέρ᾽ ἐσθλὸν ἐνὶ φρεσίν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1:115\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.115</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:20:81\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20.81</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n75576.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">presage, have foreboding of,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κακὰ δ᾽ ὄσσετο θυμός</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:10:374\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.374</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:18:154\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.154</biblScope> </bibl> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὄσσοντο γὰρ ἄλγεα θυμῷ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:18:224\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.224</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n75576.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> by imparting such presages to others, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">forebode,</tr_> used only of evil, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὡς ὅτε πορφύρῃ πέλαγος μέγα κύματι κωφῷ ὀσσόμενον λιγέων ἀνέμων λαιψηρὰ κέλευθα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:14:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.17</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; esp. by look or mien, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κάκ᾽ ὀσσόμενος</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">boding</tr_> evil <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">by his looks,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:105\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.105</biblScope> </bibl> ; of two eagles, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὄσσοντο ὄλεθρον</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">boded</tr_> death, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:2:152\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.152</biblScope> </bibl> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐ μὲν γάρ τοι ἐγὼ κακὸν ὀσσομένη τόδ᾽ ἱκάνω</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:24:172\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.172</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg001.perseus-grc1:551\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S: